This file exists so xmonad doesn't pollute `$HOME` after recompiling.

`xmonad --recompile` will ignore the presence of `$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/xmonad` and 
use `$HOME/.xmonad`, unless `$XDG_DATA_HOME/xmonad` exists.

Source: 
 * <https://github.com/xmonad/xmonad/issues/164>
 * <https://github.com/xmonad/xmonad/issues/148#issuecomment-422563425>
